pd_0_com_0text: You opened the door! Great! Now I will look for my dad... Even if we're both ghosts now, I'd like too see him again...
pd_1_com_0text: I am glad I could help.
pd_1_com_1text: Your dad was a kind person...
pd_3_com_0text: I am happy to be your friend.
pd_5_com_0text: Wait! I can give you some magical stuff my dad was working with. I have a weird hat that makes you super funny: dad told me that everyone believes you when you put it on. Or, I can give you these super goggles that let you see bad monster's health precisely.
pd_6_com_0text: I'll take the weird hat; I like to be the life of the party.
pd_6_com_1text: I'll take the goggles. I'll be stronger with them.
